title: Ep.5: Seahawks Playoff Hopes, Wilder Vs Fury 3, Packers Field Goal Fiasco, Jersey Giveaway, and More.
description: In this weeks episode we had slight technical difficulties with the microphones so this is the audio straight from the laptop. We talk about our 2 jersey giveaway starting NOW, wilder getting knocked out and his potential future opponents. The packers missing a total of four kicks but still somehow winning, and if the Seahawks have enough to survive without Russell Wilson.
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
